Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:16.50,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,We've spent our lives in shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.71,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Good people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:21.17,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Off the radar
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:23.50,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.46,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,As the pressure builds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:28.42,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,The doubts I had  looking back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.98,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand your reason
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.91,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,You always asked me every season
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.60,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,When all the madness is all over
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.77,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,What is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.85,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,…your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.19,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do we go? Don't need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:43.36,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep flow can we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.27,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.65,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,You cover me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:46.19,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:47.07,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your head
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:47.94,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:49.95,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk to me  I talk to you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:52.24,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gon'be our Xanadu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:54.87,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do we go? Is it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.16,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:59.00,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they lied to us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.43,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't wanna nap in the dirt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:05.70,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they lied to us We still got a lot of work
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.07,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we must beat the legion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.37,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, show the world we're human
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.43,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we must beat the legion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:15.20,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Show the world, we like it rough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:16.50,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一生都活在陰影之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.71,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:21.17,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,不會出現在雷達上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:23.50,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,我看見你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.46,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,壓力一來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:28.42,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的疑惑就會回首
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.98,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.91,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,你不論時節都問著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.60,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,此等瘋狂何時會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.77,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.85,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,…你的答案？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.19,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要往哪去？ 不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:43.36,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,J跟上就好 我們回得去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.27,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,我會掩護你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.65,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,你要掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:46.19,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,撿起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:47.07,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,掩護頭部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:47.94,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,撿起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:49.95,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說 我也跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:52.24,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的仙境不在這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:54.87,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要往哪去？ 要跟著你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.16,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,你的答案是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:59.00,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,對，我們被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.43,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可不要死在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:05.70,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,對，我們被騙了 但還有一堆事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.07,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,首先我們得打敗軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.37,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,然後才要告訴世界，我們是活生生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.43,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,首先我們得打敗軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:15.20,INTW,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴世界，我們保持強硬
